metadata.name: Untitled
metadata.description:
I moved to another country. To another city. My camera is always with me and I go to shoot on the streets. Some simple scenes, but so new to me. People in new clothes, strange walls and houses that look new for me. 
This transition I made in literally one day, moving from my usual world, to a completely new space. Not only within the country, but also within the perception, the possibilities, the desire to do something new. This series is about my transition to a new life.

This is one part of my journey. And it's just beginning. 

I purposely left the pictures untitled and did not give them numbers. The whole series is arranged in a random order. 
There is no main picture, but if you own two or three of the pictures in the series, you may notice how they fit together. How to put them together is up to you. 

All pictures in this series are 1/1 
You become the owner of an JPG in high resolution.
